M = (X+Y)/2
2M = X+Y \implies p_{2M}(t) = (p_X*p_Y)(t) 
p_{2M}(t)=\frac{1}{2\pi}\int_\infty^\infty \left(\exp{-\frac{(x-t)^2}{2}}\right) \left(\exp{-\frac{(x-1)^2}{2}}\right) dx
 = \frac{e^{-\frac{1}{4} (t-1)^2}}{2 \sqrt{\pi }}
